{% extends "_base.j2" %}

{% block physics_section %}
MOVEMENT
You move relative to your facing direction. MOVE_FORWARD advances one cell in the
direction you face. TURN_LEFT and TURN_RIGHT rotate you 90 degrees counter-clockwise
and clockwise respectively. Bumping into a wall does nothing (you stay in place).

PICKUP, DROP, TOGGLE, and DONE are no-ops in this environment.

OPTIMAL STRATEGY HINT
The shortest path from the top-left to the bottom-right of a 5x5 room requires
moving forward to the far wall, turning, and moving forward again. Minimize turns
and wasted steps to maximize your reward.
{% endblock %}
